name: Curated
definition: Compound structure, name, and other properties have been evaluated through a documented process for a database or library.

name: Empirical
definition: Structure has been measured and derived empirically through a peer-reviewed process.

name: Inferred
definition: Structure that is a homolog (differing in CF2 chain lengths) of an empirically-derived structure, but has not been observed empirically.

name: In Silico
definition: Structure has been predicted through documented in silico processes, but has not been observed empirically.

name: Documented
definition: Structure has been reported in documentation (e.g., patent, safety data sheet), but has not been observed empirically.

name: Limited
definition: Limited information to support structure, only a formula exists
